<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178404>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Jodis orientalis Wehrli. 1, male, syntype; 2, labels on syntype; 3, male genitalia, aedeagus removed; 4, aedeagus; 5, eighth abdominal sternite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178404/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178405>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 11. Aoshakuna lucia Thierry-Mieg, adults. 6 – 7, Aoshakuna lucia lucia Thierry-Mieg: 6, male; 7, female. 8 – 11, Aoshakuna lucia ussurica ssp. n.: 8, male; 9, female; 10, head; 11, wing venation." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178405/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178409>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Putative phylogeny of the selected genera of Hemitheini. Numbers right of internodes correspond to numbers of apomorphies in Table 1. Position of Aoshakuna Matsumura indicated by bold." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178409/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

